{"word":"G4982 - σώζω - sṓzō - sode'-zo - Heal","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σώζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sṓzō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>sode'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இரட்சி, சொஸ்தமாகு, ஆரோக்கியம் அடை, சுகமடை தப்பிப்போ, இரட்சிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to save, to keep safe and sound, to rescue from danger or destruction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a primary word <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C9;&#x0342;&#x03C2;</b> <b>so&#x0304;s&#x0304;</b> (contraction for the obsolete <b>&#x03C3;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>saos</b>, &ldquo;safe&rdquo;); to <i>save</i>, that is, <i>deliver</i> or <i>protect</i> (literally or figuratively): - heal, preserve, save (self), do well, be (make) whole."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4982 - σώζω - sṓzō - sode'-zo/4982\">G4982</a>, <a href=\"#/G4990 - σωτήρ - sōtḗr - so-tare'/4990\">G4990</a>, <a href=\"#/G4991 - σωτηρία - sōtēría - so-tay-ree'-ah/4991\">G4991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4992 - σωτήριον - sōtḗrion - so-tay'-ree-on/4992\">G4992</a>"}]}